 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx} by homotopy and identity homotopies is univalent.

Given a dependent function f : \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
