}}{Bx}, if each component Bx is contractible with centre fx then the dependent product \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
